Description: Condition: This Reverend Warhawk 390 in Korina Burst is in excellent condition. It shows little to no signs of wear, and was used very little. The Warhawk 390 delivers the P90 bite you know and love, with the addition of two and four on the 5-way pickup selector to give you classic "quack" and thicker tone with midrange presence. It features a thicker raised center on its korina body, which increases body mass, while the thinner wings increase resonance for incredible sustain and harmonics. The guitar is stacked with 9A5 pickups in the bridge, middle, and neck, and is equipped with a Bigsby B50.
